    "source": "Altimetry: Sentinel 3 Thematic Sea Ice Product - baseline 5, Snow depth: ESA-SICCI AMSR-E/AMSR2 snow depth on sea ice climatology, Mean Sea Surface: DTU21 global mean sea surface, Sea ice Concentration: C3S Sea Ice Concentration CDR/ICDR v3.0, Sea ice type: First-year sea ice only, Region code: Longitude-based sectors from Parkinson, C. L. and Cavalieri, D. J. (2012)",
